<u>Help on Question Grading:</u><br/> 
Certain questions are automatically graded. To correct an ungraded question either click on the <img align="bottom" border="0" src="/graphics/quiz/correct_small.gif"/> or <img align="bottom" border="0" src="/graphics/quiz/incorrect_small.gif"/> The correct answer will receive full points; the incorrect answer will receive no points. To enter partial or bonus points, type the points granted in the box. 
